{2: 'System', 3: 'Rebooting... System rebooted.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Mission information updated.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Mission level: High, Hazard: High, Clearance: High, Insufficient mission data.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Please authenticate your identity.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Fingerprint authenticated. Identity: 【kuroname】.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Region Number: 049, Region Type: Ruined City, Locational data retrieval failed, unable to download region map.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Mission details confirmation check. Mission already assigned, cannot reassign mission. Please confirm again.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Confirmation failed.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Commandant, what's the matter?", 4: '1'}
{2: "Looks like there's a system error.", 3: '17'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "It's a high-security clearance mission, so it's got restrictions. It should be okay now.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Hmm? It says the mission is ongoing. Has it been accepted or checked before?', 4: '1'}
{2: "I don't think so.", 3: '22', 4: "I don't remember.", 5: '22'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Commandant, I read the mission information.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'The mission brief mentions that most individual Constructs sent to City 049 from Babylonia went missing within a day or two.', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Lucia', 3: "They seem to have been attacked by an unknown source. Only a few survivors managed to recall in time. Their consciousness data are still under analysis and repair, so there isn't enough info.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'HQ wants the Gray Raven squad to investigate City 049 under the command network of Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'From what I can see, the mission is indeed not yet accepted.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Regarding this error about the mission status, can you try to repair it, Lee?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Systems are normal. As for the mission authentication, only Commandant has access to it, there shouldn't be anyone else...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "I know what's wrong.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Replaying video information of central control room. Time: Before system reboot.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Commandant! Commandant!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami's got a new shiny frame! I wanted you to see it first!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "These super-duper-cooler IR-005 wheels are fitted in by Nanami herself! Hmm... No one's here?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'New emergency mission. Mission level: High, Hazard: High, Clearance: High, Insufficient mission data.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'High hazard? Are they giving some strange mission to Commandant again?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Please authenticate your identity.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hm...? Hm-hm...? Nanami needs to put her finger here?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Authentication failed.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'PULSE! ARMOR! TRANS—FORM!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "...Okay fine, Nanami can't transform.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "It's so boring here without Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hmmm... Ahah... then... Nanami will just... got it!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Unknown authentication method. Authenticated. Identity: Unknown.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Yep, yep. Nanami understands it a hundred and ten percent.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Commandant has to leave for missions again right after returning.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hm... If that's the case...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Then Nanami will just finish this mission before Commandant comes back! Haha!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami! Preparing for launch!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Ah! Right! Almost forgot! I need to leave a note for the commandant!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Pulse Construct, Nanami, blast off!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Replay has ended.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "I don't think she understood a single percent of what she read.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Where was the last message left?', 3: '82', 4: 'Have more faith.', 5: '82'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'I checked the entire system.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "...And there's a comment by Nanami written in the underlying core architecture...", 4: '1'}
{3: '"Commandant, Nanami\'s on a mission! Wait for Nanameeee! (<ゝω?)☆"'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Lee, do you know what that symbol at the end means? I can't find any relevant information in the database, and it might be an important message from Nanami.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "No dice. I'll need some time to decipher it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'No need to investigate that.', 3: '93', 4: "It's just a cute emoticon.", 5: '93'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Understood, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "My database on the corpus of human culture is not as wide as Nanami's... How can this be...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Commandant, most of the Constructs losing contact moved on their own to investigate war zone 049.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "That should be why HQ wants us to move in as a team, with Commandant as well to ensure our safety. But now Nanami's out there on her own...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'I believe in Nanami.', 3: '102', 4: 'That is a bit worrying.', 5: '104'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "I agree, though she's uncontrollable, she's still a powerful ally to have on our side.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Commandant... should we go take a look?'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "But, from the video replay, that new frame of Nanami's—Pulse, seems to be installed with two new acceleration boosters. To catch up with her wouldn't be easy.", 4: '1'}
